<#
.SYNOPSIS
Configures the interactive logon legal banner (LegalNoticeText) with the required U.S. Government warning.

.NOTES
Author          : Sultan Jarad
LinkedIn        : https://www.linkedin.com/in/sultan-jarad/
GitHub          : https://github.com/sultancyber
Date Created    : 2025-09-17
Last Modified   : 2025-09-17
Version         : 1.0
CVEs            : N/A
Plugin IDs      : N/A
STIG-ID         : WN11-SO-000075

.TESTED ON
Date(s) Tested  :
Tested By       :
Systems Tested  :
PowerShell Ver. :

.USAGE
Apply the related registry setting for this STIG.
Example:
PS C:> .\WN11-SO-000075.ps1
#>
# Configure interactive logon legal banner
$regPath = 'HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System'
if (-not (Test-Path $regPath)) { New-Item -Path $regPath -Force | Out-Null }
Set-ItemProperty -Path $regPath -Name 'LegalNoticeCaption' -Value '*** USG Warning Notice ***' -Type String
Set-ItemProperty -Path $regPath -Name 'LegalNoticeText'    -Value 'You are accessing a U.S. Government (USG) Information System...' -Type String
